&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manager, Customer Success&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Manager, Customer Success, you will hire and develop teams, coaching Customer Success Managers (CSMs) to success. This role impacts our customer experience and retention at scale, providing an opportunity to join a company that’s a leader in the space and see your contributions firsthand. At Datadog, we value our office culture—the relationships and collaboration it builds, and the creativity it inspires. We operate as a hybrid workplace to help our Datadogs create a work-life harmony that best fits them.&lt;/p&gt;
