&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally to drive positive customer outcomes and solve complex challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on talent attraction, retention, and development to create high-performance teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
